    <item>
      <title>耶伦表示美国可以选择保护工业免受中国侵害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/yellen-says-us-has-option-to-shield-new-industries-against-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，在中国在清洁能源等领域进行大规模国家投资后，美国将保留保护新工业部门免受中国影响的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/yellen-says-us-has-option-to-shield-new-industries-against-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 20:33:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列甘茨向内塔尼亚胡提高赌注，呼吁提前选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/israel-s-gantz-ups-ante-with-netanyahu-by-calling-for-early-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列战时内阁成员本尼·甘茨呼吁提前举行选举，这加大了对​​总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡的压力。随着加沙冲突愈演愈烈，国内针对其政府的抗议活动日益增多，内塔尼亚胡正面临国际社会的强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/israel-s-gantz-ups-ante-with-netanyahu-by-calling-for-early-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 19:34:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克向泰晤士水务公司施压以清理自己的财务混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/sunak-presses-thames-water-to-clean-up-its-own-financial-mess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克政府正在敦促泰晤士水务公司及其陷入困境的母公司单独解决其财务困难，这增加了英国最大水务公司面临的危机将在未来几周内加深的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/sunak-presses-thames-water-to-clean-up-its-own-financial-mess</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:18:51 GMT</pubDate>
